data.description: Granada, Pool Home Beauty! 3 car garage. Solar. There's nothing left to do, Owner spared no expense in updating & customizing w/high end features. Heated Pool is less than 1 year new. New luxury vinyl plank flooring & 5 inch baseboards throughout. Chef kitchen is stylish w/ custom cabinets w/designer colors.  Counters have Leathered Granite (Dolimite), stone backsplash, enlarged island w/deep sink. Thor Gas cooktop, Thermador oven, and New LG Studio Fridge.  Corner walk in pantry with a repurposed antique door. The butler pantry includes beverage cooler, lots of cabinets & serving area. Master Bathroom is stunning w/tile & stone designs in walk in shower.  Huge walk in closet. Whole house water filtration system. You need to touch & feel this home to enjoy the  beauty of all the amenities
